      "content": "# versioning operations on document models are not implemented\n\nThe document model operation taxonomy includes a \"Versioning\" category, but it is explicitly marked as not implemented. Do not use any versioning-related operations — they will fail or produce undefined behavior.\n\nThis is a known gap in the current system. Version management for document models must be handled through other means (e.g., git versioning of the source files).\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[gotchas]]\n- [[architecture decisions]]",
